  "content": {
    "prompt": "Using recursion, complete the sum1toN method so that it returns the total sum of all numbers from 1 to N.\nExamples:\n\n\n    sum1toN(3) => 6\n\n    sum1toN(5) => 15",
    "source_code": "public class JRecursionSum1{\n    int sum1toN(int n){\n        if(n > 0){\n            return n + sum1toN(n-1);\n        }\n        return 0;  \n    }\n    \n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        JRecursionSum1 rs = new JRecursionSum1();\n        int n = 10;\n        System.out.println(\"Sum of 10 Numbers is: \"+rs.sum1toN(n));\n    }\n}"
  },
